&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700; text-decoration-line: underline;&quot;&gt;Наполнитель:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;100% иглопробивной лен&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.6;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.6;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700; text-decoration-line: underline;&quot;&gt;Ткань обшивки:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 100% хлопок, плотность 250 гр./м2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.6;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700; text-decoration-line: underline;&quot;&gt;Вид крепления:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;резинки по углам изделия&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.6;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700; text-decoration-line: underline;&quot;&gt;Цвет:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;кремо